                    <span>... then read this book. Kushner has done a simply excellent job at writing this book. It is laid out in a simple, chronological manner, very well informed and fun to read.
<br />The story of the two Johns and the rest of the iD staff, the living legends of the fps genre. Need I say more?
<br />Read this book!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">You don't have to play Doom to love this book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
